" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_3_4_9_11" target="w1_3_4_9_11_12"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="603" y="1562"/><mxPoint x="621" y="1609"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e11" value="deny moral realism" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#c0392b;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_3_4_9" target="w1_3_4_9_14"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="332" y="1357"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1712"/><mxPoint x="146" y="1712"/><mxPoint x="182" y="1816"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e12" value="only this moment&#x27;s feeling is real" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#c0392b;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_3_4_9" target="w1_3_4_9_15"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="302" y="1341"/><mxPoint x="137" y="1418"/><mxPoint x="137" y="1418"/><mxPoint x="137" y="1418"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1471"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1951"/><mxPoint x="72" y="1951"/><mxPoint x="84" y="2055"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><object label="Parochial&lt;br&gt;community + nation&lt;br&gt;→ Local soup kitchen&lt;br&gt;(common-sense default)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Least-crazy end of the line. What matters is humans in my family and local community, in the present generation. Distant strangers, animals and the future are outside the circle (weight 0), so the local option wins. The soup kitchen&#x27;s value is a worked BOTEC — people made happier per dollar times their wellbeing gain, netted against the counterfactual of the money sitting in a bank — and every worldview downstream imports that agreed number unchanged. The pre-EA commonsense baseline; no single EA figure defends it. || Chain: 0 parochial" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1VW1v2kgQ%2FisjdFUhIsTQtL2j4gME50WlbZRyV53iSFnsMd7retfaXeO4af77zdokQDCf4jAzz7w9z%2BxjK8KY5cKeqQhbw9bJCYxGI5hrxiVYBaFmv0r6KCQE%2BcDrn0KhtIhWHAsoPGgbqzLwOi4okBQ8NiZPM8uVhDAhjCF4kDGtwoQzUXn4LEyAbdy4AQbXpU3oO%2BYCgRJvzOYEbMIssCgyXdBI1XKJBpSuwDQeEzpL0aLmhn63CdaJ3xqIcxlWGJ8gVGmmDJfLjQPFyggJkX7ipkIzlsmICSURUhqH6MH9S7f%2B6t6V6sLxIcPQUuCKiRxBxRXCZjC9CmyCxsIiLyF3aVygwe3GhjBTIRNgVJ7BT27DBGUdeeF%2F9W%2FGc38KixKWKFEzi72sfN4ARtzujOiIjF2QytaFuCkSUoU15ZpqBYxj94dGjG78Si9pPpnmKdMlLChFzENO312Y%2BOffbnzqX6%2F3VSBfJpZGR9MQynEi4ff11oRaSqVTauIv7w2cXUFbaer1WMXHKVtKbvMIYfJt7p91qB7X6Oe6zykT5TXqv00EI3gMJECGKhN4iSLD6MXi9bz3LqHXe%2B98ChRigVTJBa3PQdQuXr%2F28frOKVS5JDLELLQ5ExMmf%2F5Tbcm5vjuQ6agB%2BgjafTg%2BBNcJ5FMgl9FOI64W73RdjDcIJEvjPYd36468AZXLeLrn8NzNgHq2idix93sDZz39SNMssl3TwPOc7eMpFRHIgotokS%2FNrs%2BH2ufPQeXDhIhxv4XBy8hJHIVSrz0qu0Pw1hzzb4vpePYvsBVqJ4uM6P7H3XCbatEODS1P11Ld0CxUZCQSorSv5ETh7NVVgSy3xrGZW0esUDkZj%2BDW7fcRaO44hKC1r6%2Bg1YUiemlnCCky2W4kZocY0Ien7i7kBV9hLSlRNoNtc8JheI0YP4hv4E4ntaO5LaE9%2FnLeaUbcYVEz5PjqC5zA2RrLl1ZjRucNc20Snh2A3eZeM%2BycNnSZp4zu4QzZMsdmpB2WNiN9T%2BjWZEBtx0wjXGv1H83wwDq2md0M94PYTe%2BEIQwD7aQuMaODSwSK0BwY5L4mDkxzNjv3pwem9kozh%2FYBhsXo9npTawhu6PwzHSYHatuT2gb4zslM0%2BVxz9cIZtzYnkbSmsF29Y9R2k7Kdi2DLjz%2BfvgND72tHE8dulcL9x6NYA10692t1TtvfNHml1ffNxIcQuEeYU7TXjw%2FayRuTlUYEuDWI0kZnMd29kC2nv4HzvjYeg%3D%3D" id="w0"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#dfe7ef;strokeColor=#6b7f96;fontColor=#1b2733;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="696" y="0" width="186" height="92" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="All present humans&lt;br&gt;count equally&lt;br&gt;[1]&lt;br&gt;→ GiveWell top charity (AMF)&lt;br&gt;(Alexander Berger, Peter Singer)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A life saved abroad counts like a life saved at home, so cheap, measurable global-health and cash interventions dominate. Alexander Berger is the prominent exemplar of deliberately getting off the train here and staying with robust, evidence-backed global health &amp; wellbeing. The soup kitchen&#x27;s agreed BOTEC is still carried through untouched; it is simply no longer the best buy. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Ve9v2zYQ%2FVcOxoY5geNIbrquHvzBjpUfmLsGqbdiiIKGlk4WV4oUSMqKluZ%2F31FyYjuWP0Xx3T3evXuPfOrEmLBC2HMVY2fYOT2F0WgEc824BKsg0uy%2Fij5KCWEx8PwzKJUW8YpjCaUPXWNVDv6RKwolFY%2BNKbLcciUhSgljCB7kTKso5Uw4CP%2FjAHxImP7GSlZ9S4uMSVOXBixKgW3quQEGN5VN6TvhAoE62oTNKdiUWWBxbHqgkcbgEg0oXYNpPKFjWYYWNTf0u02x6egXA0khoxrjd4hUlivD5XKTQLUyRkKkn3jTmrFMxkwoiZART6IPD680BKsH16orx8ccI0uFKyYKBJXUCBvG%2BjXYBI2FRVFB4Y5xhQa3BxvCJV%2FhVxQCHLnUk%2Ba2gu7408VRg3AZ%2FBncjufBFBYVLFGiZhb7efWyIoy53aHqmII9kMo2DTk2CanGmnJNPQMmiftDVKNbg9JL4inXPGO6ggUdkfCI03cPJsHF59uAeNBM1Agl8mVqiUJiRSgnmpQ%2FNNsTaimVzmjzH72f4fwaukrTzCcqOcnYUnJbxAiTz%2FPg3E1mVJH%2FwW2UopwyUd2g%2FsvEMIKnUALkqHKBVyhyjF8jXt977w70%2Bu9dTkmcLZA6uaQ1OogmxfObHM93SZEqJIkiYZEtmJgw%2Bf3velsu9d2Bk45boI%2Bh68PJIbijUD6HchnvDOJ68c7WzXiDULIs2Ut4t57IG1C7jGd7CS%2FTDGhmm4qduN8fuOjZB2KzzHdDA89zsQ9n1EQoSy7iRbE0uzm%2FNjm%2FDeocJkSC%2ByMMXiknk5RKvc2o4w7BW2ssuCun49k%2FwFaonT1ykv1P98NtqcU7MrQ8W1t2I7NIUZBEiNK%2BsRWVszfXDuSFNU7N3DphRcrZeQR3br9PQLzjEMLOTEUkTSc7%2BN7oLuz0oIxfxxlChkx2W4V5RArw4bm3C%2Bms21hKVO1g25o4jNFu%2F3bEHRW1Q46vP8EpnK%2BxAmk15nTNYaFNyvMDsNvaa4ed04au3A2OMEO2LLAdaUelDsnbQ%2FqS0l2TA41NTwPCjVb%2FEocH1rGt7Ha4r6Ruei8MYRjopk2LOV28JKAYzQEi9z3Rjj6ezS6C6QHW3njmAMI1GJag2%2Btt4yG4pWeA6Sg90Nue1TbA985mmm4e94yNYMaN7Wskrxns1v8Ype2k6jY26MHTj8cf8NjfOuP5iO6rhXuXRrAGuvPu1%2B6dt75s86vrLxsLDqF0jzEnthcvzxuZm1MXhgy49VjSCS5j%2B%2FRQdp7%2FB6%2Ba4vc%3D" id="w1"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#cfe6cf;strokeColor=#5a9367;fontColor=#1e3a24;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="660" y="223" width="258" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Animals count&lt;br&gt;(neuron-weighted)&lt;br&gt;[1+2]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;▼ 111 more worldviews" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Farmed vertebrates enter the circle, weighted by a sentience-adjusted welfare range (neuron-count exponent). Corporate welfare campaigns avert enormous suffering per dollar and overtake human global health under most welfare-range estimates. An animals person won&#x27;t think only people in their community matter, so this assumption requires far_away_humans. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2.drawio" id="w1_2"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#e6e2c0;strokeColor=#b0a04a;fontColor=#3a3410;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="755" y="462" width="179" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Future humans count&lt;br&gt;(discounted)&lt;br&gt;[1+3]&lt;br&gt;→ GiveWell top charity (AMF)&lt;br&gt;(Frank Ramsey, Tyler Cowen)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Future people are inside the circle, but with a positive pure-time discount rate — the moderate longtermist position. A modest discount is enough to keep present, measurable global health competitive with future-protecting work; remove it (the next assumption) and the astronomical numbers take over. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playgrou