winter or an abrupt sunlight-reduction catastrophe) does more far-future good than marginal AGI-safety funding — it is more neglected and more tractable while buying the same astronomical future. The longtermist winner flips from AI safety to ALLFED. A within-longtermism reallocation, so it requires no_discounting_future_humans. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 9 living_in_simulation → 11 person_affecting_view → 12 resilient_foods_beat_agi" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1lW1z4jYQx7%2FKDtNOIUOIbbi7hg4vSEIe5rheJkd70wkZR9hrrJ4seSQZh%2Bby3buyIYEA78C7%2Bmkf%2Frt6bsSYsELYcxVjo984OYHBYAATzbgEqyDS7L8l%2FSglTIvA83tQKi3iBccSSj%2Fshr3wNPT90A%2BgaazKwQ9ajjCVRBoaU2S55UpClBKwDx7kTKso5Uw4nn8agA8J0yEr2TJMi4xJszZ0ISlsoXH1OcyYtajDkts0jLmJVCEtl%2FO1ew%2Bk2vwebp1ee52C4Atn5TI0PCsEq8Jbx%2BJDjtooGbIkwajCVKmu7QFoNFxwlDZMlIpNOENmQzbnVcIjFqXA3rLmBhjcLm1KvxMuEKiob2ZzAjZlFlgcmzaBqRNcogGlK5jGYyoWy5Cy5oa%2B2xTrOv5mqDQyqhh%2FQKSyXBlXiVcHOitjJCJ94qaiGctkzISSCBm1WnTg8bWTo8WjC9Udx6ec8qaDCyYKBJVUhLemdyrYGRoLs2IJhbvGHTS4mVgfhuPx5eii9r4a%2FTm6G05GFzBbwhwlamaxky%2FXisKY262yHJGxTe209eWuckSqWBdcU3yAVXuAyoqu5ErPqSa55hnTS5jRFQmPOP1uw9no8uvdiHLWTFSEEvk8dZ2lCgjlNJ7yx7pTQs2l0hlp89T7Fc5voKk05XeskuOMzSW3RYxw9nUyOm9RPEYV%2BWduoxTlBRPLW9R%2FmRgG8DyVQDJSucBrFDnGrxav431wF3qdD86nRCFmSJFcUcsconbx%2FNrH851TJWfUCYtswcQZkz%2F%2BrjrjXLsHbjragz6Cpg%2FHh3CtqXyZynm8lYiLxeutgvGCqWRZsuPQXWXkBRQu49mOwzqbgHK2qdiy%2B53AWXufqJplvm0KPM%2FZPvUoiKksuYhnxdxs%2B3ysfX4PKh8mRIK7KQSvJaeBKGlo33lUdkfwVhob3ZcXw%2FE%2FwBao3SjQSoBfHvqbUou3ZGh5thrPN5lFiowkQtoU70aIjrN3ixHywhqnZm6dsCLlRncA966%2Fz0B1xz5MG2MVkTSd7OBHrbtpow1l%2FJpOHzJksrlXmC1SgA8v7W3kFV9gPVJiuR%2B2qYnDjO%2BkN3Drn9LR3C6hOfxy2dpP3FLRfuTw5gucwPmKNZJWY04rDQttUp4fwG5qbz92Qh26ds8BwhjZvMD9pC2VOpK3Q%2FqW0q7JgdKmxwvhVqt%2FqYYH2rGp7P2476RuehsMMQw00zrEnJYsCShGc6CQuzOxn17v4h1G1%2B2ECrQzF47TxWPvY2tPa8CwBF2L7%2BpjcEfbn%2BkoPRDmYXoFf3BTp2kRuRdsAGNubEcjjZ7BZvXHKG3Pls16Ktrw%2FPPpJzx1Nu5