han a person with a past and a future, the only thing that registers is whatever you happen to feel right now. Every charity collapses to the same low pleasant-thought level of value; the ranking goes flat and no donation beats any other. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 9 living_in_simulation → 15 boltzmann_brain" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJydVW1v2zgM%2FitEsMOlRZraabqtOeRDX9IXLLsVXe6GQ124ik3HusmSIclxva7%2FfZSdpEm7AZf7FEckH5EPH4qPrRgTVgh7qmJsDVr7%2BzAcDmGiGZdgFUSafavoo5QQFD3P70OptIjnHEso%2FfAg7IdHoX8IbWNVDv7hjgsPJMEcG1NkueVKQpQS2gA8yJlWUcqZcGD%2BUQ98SJgOWcmqMC0yJs3ScABJYQuNi%2BMwY9aiDktu0zDmJlKFtFzOlu59kGr9PNyIXnodgeBzZ%2BUyNDwrBKvTW%2BZyCFMl7DeKkOHUEVDXMWJRCuy5GG6AwXVlU%2FpOuEAgop7NZh9syiywODYd0EjscokGlK7BNO4RByxDKoYbOrcpNvT8bqhiGdUYf0CkslwZV%2BDKgWJljIRIR9zUaMYyGTOhJEJG7RNduF91ZzS%2Fd6m6cHzIMbIUOGeiQFBJjfDcyG4NdoLGwrSooHDXuECD64UNiGKKazh3QtBMfnV%2FE6KxgbgY%2FTm6OZ6MzmBawQwlamaxm1fLCIy53eBql4wdh9tk5OgkpECu%2BjDGOQoYgo97bwHoCldrIhDr5ucCmWHSRatiltqO60V5djz%2BZ%2F9N0HTvjGuqHTBJ3A%2B1DF07lZ4R37nmGdMVTCnThEecvjtwMjr%2FdDMiPjUTNUKJnKDpOmJXKDcTKb9vVCDUTCqdkZyPvN%2Fg9AraShN3eyrZy9hMclvECCefJqPTHSrLqCL%2FwG2UojxjorpG%2FZeJqbbHQALkqKiaSxQ5xiuL1%2FUO3YVe99D5lCjEFCmTC5KDg2hcPL%2Fx8XznVE8A6oRFtmDihHr0d91153rwi5t2fwK9C20f9n4FtxPIp0DO4o1CXC5ef5GM1wsky5JXDgeLirwepct49sphWU2Parap2LD73Z6z9t8Rm2W%2Baep5nrO961MSgSy5iKfFzGz6vG183vdqHyZEgq9L6K0op2ErlXrpUdsdgrfQ2Oi21hywOWo3ZjmNz5u7wbrU4g0ZWp4tRv9ZZpEiI4kQpX0xnhTOXrylkBfWODVzN3n06rlnYQi3rr%2BPQLzjAILWWEUkTSc7%2BNroLmh1oIxX5QzgxaA9dTYRLvgcmwkS1f%2BJ%2FUKyArcYKGvNbQXt44%2FnO9siHV99hH04XUCMpNWY02OIhTYpz7dFmxDtl24tIIyRzQrcFuBzSu9GDlQb7S6Ea63%2BJYK2RflCAqXnylCogXbaJJTTG0waiNFsT9J4fD46255aMCxB15mbRuxwQ%2B8%2B01H6nzK4cyOwXARDGHNju5qs2mC7%2FmOUtidVu5FoBx6%2FP3yHh%2B4a7NMOvSVTt3uGy41y690tJmvy0%2B01ubz6%2FDweAyjdwuVE43S5wmjwOGVhaDjWFiLd4DzWbw9k6%2BkHoa4Yxw%3D%3D" id="w1_3_4_9_15"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="0" y="2135" width="200" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Person-affecting&lt;br&gt;view&lt;br&gt;[1+3+4+11]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;(Jan Narveson, Melinda Roberts)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 11 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1lW1z4jYQx7%2FKDtNOIUOIDVyvR4cXJHEeplwvk6O96YQMEfYaq2dLHkmO4%2Bby3buyeXIw78C7%2Bmkf%2Frt6bQUYsiw2FzLA1qh1dgbj8RhminEBRoKv2H8F%2FcgFzLO%2B4w4hlyoOnjnmkLuLwWK4cF1oayNTcN2OPTwXBJlonSWp4VKAHxFrBA6kTEk%2F4iy2KPdTH1wImVqwnBWLKEuY0BvDAMLMZArXnxcJMwbVIucmWgRc%2BzIThovVxn0IQu5%2FX9ROb29zIUWlpViwMES%2FdLR5lPF6zI%2BA7YLmGhjcFSai3yGPEagcO7M%2BAxMxAywIdBcUUg25QA1SlTCFp5QrS5CC5pq%2BmwirMvyiKTPhl4zfwZdJKrVNZOtAZ0WARKRPXJc0bZgIWCwFQkJNinvwtO2B9%2FxkQ7XH8SWlpOjgM4szBBmWhF27eiXsHLWBZVZAZq%2BxBzXuJzaCyS1oFqIpoH2PQS5lAPfkxJQfdSrGtfendz%2BZeZewLGCFAhUz2EuLjUIw4KZWrBMydqlHpgrJ1pNIJeuSK4oasOwIULHRNkKqFVUqVTxhqoAlXRFyn9PvLpx7V1%2FuPaqEYnFJyJGvIttMqkssrWYj%2FlT1L5YrIVVCgvvk%2FAwXt9CWirI%2BleFpwlaCmyxAOP8y8y5sZlpm6R%2Fc%2BBGKSxYXd6j%2B0gGM4XUugJQj0xhvME4x2FqcnvPBXuj0PlifHON4iRTJ